<div class="app-card-about">
  <div class="card">
    <!-- <h1>About me</h1>
    <hr> -->
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile_image.jpg", width: 300, alt:"Profile image",class:"profile-image img-responsive"%>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <h1 class="cover-heading">About Me.</h1>
        <p class="about-me-text">A web developer and trainer. Life long learner.
          I co-founded <a href="www.therailshop.club">Therailsshop</a>,
          a creative space for kids aged 11+ years old to learn how to code. <a href="www.therailshop.club">Therailsshop</a>
          also doubles as a web studio specializing in building ruby on rails 
          powered back-end apis and Angular 4 front-end applications.
          <br> <br> Click <a href="www.therailshop.club">
            here</a> to learn more about the kids coding club.
      </p>
          <section id="about-me-social">
              <span><a href="https://facebook.com/TheRailsShop" 
                target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-facebook fa-2x"></i></a></span>
              <span><a href="https://twitter.com/Railsshop" 
                 target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-twitter fa-2x"></i></a></span>
              <span><a href="https://www.quora.com/profile/Alex-Nkusi-Shyaka"
                 target="_blank""><i class="fa fa-quora fa-2x"></i ></a></span>
                  <span><a href="http://www.alexshyaka.site"
                 target="_blank""><i class="fa fa-rss fa-2x"></i ></a></span>
          </section>
          
      <p>
         <button
           class="btn btn-primary"
           type="button"
           data-toggle="collapse"
           data-target="#jobHistory"
           aria-expanded="false"
           aria-controler="jobHistory"
         >
           Job History
         </button>

         <button
           class="btn btn-primary"
           type="button"
           data-toggle="collapse"
           data-target="#education"
           aria-expanded="false"
           aria-controler="education"
         >
           Education
         </button>
       </p>

       <p>
         <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
           <div class="card card-block">
              Founder: <a href="https://www.therailsshop.club">Therailsshop Company LTD.</a>
              A Web skills training and development studio.I aim to build a
              community of web developers that collaborates and learns 
              together. The purpose of the community is to build
              and incubate business ideas.
           </div>
           <div class="card card-block">
              Business development: Panya Tech:
              Reaching out and on-boarding Small and Medium sized
              enterprises to our online platform that aggregates
               products and services in Kampala.

           </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
                Web Developer: Polaris Health Directions, Inc. USA: 
                Software development, Data extraction, survey development using
                ABBY FlexiCapture.

              </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
                  .NET application developer: Progressive Consulting Technologies
                  A Microsoft. NET shop.
              </div>
          
         </div>

         <div class="collapse" id="education">
           <div class="card card-block">
             <a href="https://www.freecodecamp.org" target="_blank">FreeCodeCamp</a> Front-End certification: on-going.
           </div>
           <div class="card card-block">
             Sikkim manipal University: BSC Applied Information Technology.
             
           </div>
           <div class="card card-block">
             London school of computer technology: Diploma Software Engineering.
           </div>
         </div>
       </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
